# Company: Unikraft

- Website: https://unikraft.org
- Founder(s): Felipe Huici
- Location: EU / Global
- Primary Category: Cloud Infrastructure

## What they do
Unikraft builds lightweight unikernels for cloud-native workloads.

## Target user (ICP)
Infra engineers, performance-focused teams.

## Key features
- Unikernels
- Faster boot times
- Lower resource usage

## Pricing
Open-source + enterprise

## Positioning
“Build fast, secure cloud workloads.”

## Overlap with Clode
